    "body": "Stasrhip does not suppress conda's own prompt modifier, you may want to run `conda config --set changeps1 False`.\r\n\r\nPlease also try disabling the other prompts in your zshrc to avoid interference and potential performance issues.\r\n\r\nIf the problem persists, please post the output of `starship explain`.",
