    "updated_at": "2024-10-16T05:21:12Z",
    "body": "Okay, I resolve the issue. The cause was the default style, `bold green`. It looks like there is no bold `conda` symbol in some font families. When I set the style just to `green`, the symbol is rendered as expected.",
